result.name: The Coffee Academics Sai Ying Pun

reviews.text: I am asking myself why they have a food menu? - Do not recommend the food it is really not how you expect it to be. Lobster roll was not lobster or similar, it was plastic. For 200HK$, rather do a shrimp roll, cheaper and easier to make. Pizza is not pizza, it’s flatbread not really crispy. Really just come here for coffee and not more.

Location wise: right next to exit B3 is Sai Ying Pun station. 
I ordered a cup of Manuka latte. It was smooth but not too strong. 
Ps: Companion commented it as a welcoming place for customers who work or linger there.

Nice environment with not too many ppl on holiday! 
Just my iced tea is a bit... unique 😅

After drinking espresso for 15+ years ... this place served up the best espresso. So incredibly smooth and cheaper than most other shops in Hong Kong. Don't miss out on this place if you are s coffee lover.  They have many locations in the city. 

The staff is very engaging at this location.
Comfortable place to meet and drink coffee!

reviews.text: It is so close to main road, and it would be very noisy and air-polluted. It is better to live like, Kings Hill, Kensington House at Western Street, or The Summa nearby. Artisan is ONLY close to mtr exit A, but so far away from the platform. Exit A, B, C are far away, exit B1, 2 is close to platform.
very very conbenient location, less than one minute you are in the metro, you will not sweat or get wet no matter what weather.
Good looking

距離皇后大道西和德輔道西每邊各有一棟樓之隔，無咁嘈。

地鐵站出口離入閘遠，不過入閘離月台近。情況剛好和舊式港島線車站設計相反。譬如銅鑼灣中環上環側魚涌站雖然出口離入閘近，入閘卻離月台遠，結果由地面出口走到車上距離沒有比這裡省時間。

大廈入口離地鐵出口30秒絕對是優勢，附近可以比較的有西蒲，寶翠園，藝里坊，翰林峰，其實選擇不是太多。而所謂地鐵站上蓋的大型項目都需要穿過會所或商場才回到家，沒有廣告裡面寫的方便。

樓價漲不停，開放式迷你戶呎價愈升愈有！新世界發展（0017）旗下西營盤新盤「瑧蓺」公布首批50伙的價單，折實平均呎價28,508元，但其中一個221平方呎開放式單位，折實後售價約802萬元﹙開價約1,003萬元﹚，呎價高達3.63萬元，挑戰同區開放戶新高。

細小單位，發展商開價如斯「進取」，樓市專家剖析箇中原因，並拆解對早已瘋狂的本港樓市的啟示。瑧蓺今次提供的第一按揭貸款高達淨樓價的80%，如果買家是專業人士，按揭貸款更高達85%。

高成數按揭，有助降低入場門檻，現在大部分港人都供得起樓，但付不起首期，在發展商提供按揭的情況下，一手市場因而暢旺。舉例，即是同樣叫價700萬元的新盤和二手樓相比，入場費因有發展商的高成數按揭，前者以8成按揭計，入場費為140萬元，但後者入場費或高達300萬元，兩者相差160萬元。
